Transformation.Name: UNIX時間
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10020" AS ( SELECT "S03_ENER", "DATETIME", "S01_ENER", "S01_FREQ", "DEVICE", "S02_FREQ", "S02_ENER", "S03_FREQ",trunc(to_number( datetime - to_date('1970/01/01 00:00:00', 'YYYY/MM/DD HH24:MI:SS') ) * (24 * 60 * 60)) as "UNIXTIME" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Transformation.Name: 信頼度の絶対値 2
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10064" AS ( SELECT "S03_ENER", "DATETIME", "S01_ENER", "S01_FREQ", "DEVICE", "S02_FREQ", "S02_ENER", "S03_FREQ", "UNIXTIME", "PROB", "PRED",CASE PRED WHEN 1 THEN PROB WHEN 0 THEN 1 - PROB END as "PROB_ABS",ABS(1 - PRED) as "PRED_INV" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

TransformationElementType.CustomTransformationEx: CASE PRED WHEN 1 THEN PROB WHEN 0 THEN 1 - PROB END

Transformation.Name: 信頼度の絶対値 1
Transformation.SQLExpression: "N$10076" AS ( SELECT "PROB", "PRED", "S03_ENER", "DATETIME", "S01_ENER", "S01_FREQ", "DEVICE", "S02_FREQ", "S02_ENER", "S03_FREQ", "UNIXTIME",CASE "PRED" WHEN 0 THEN "PROB" WHEN 1 THEN 1 - "PROB" END as "PROB_ABS" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

TransformationElementType.CustomTransformationEx: CASE "PRED" WHEN 0 THEN "PROB" WHEN 1 THEN 1 - "PROB" END

Join.Name: 結合

Apply.Name: 適用 1
Apply.SQLExpression: "N$10008" as (SELECT "S03_ENER", "DATETIME", "S01_ENER", "S01_FREQ", "DEVICE", "S02_FREQ", "S02_ENER", "S03_FREQ", "UNIXTIME", PREDICTION("CLAS_SVM_1_9" USING *) "PRED", PREDICTION_PROBABILITY("CLAS_SVM_1_9" USING *) "PROB" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )

Apply.Name: 適用 2
Apply.SQLExpression: "N$10054" as (SELECT "S03_ENER", "DATETIME", "S01_ENER", "S01_FREQ", "DEVICE", "S02_FREQ", "S02_ENER", "S03_FREQ", "UNIXTIME", PREDICTION("ANOM_SVM_1_9" USING *) "PRED", PREDICTION_PROBABILITY("ANOM_SVM_1_9" USING *) "PROB" FROM {INPUT_SOURCE} )
